N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 36.5 - Certificate made by attendant at birth

State Regulations

If the physician or licensed midwife who attended the birth is alive and can be located, the certificate shall be made by such physician or licensed midwife. Notes
